Package: peruopen
Type: Package
Title: Access Peru's Open Data Portal (CKAN)
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Horacio Chacón-Torrico <hchacont@uw.edu> [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Horacio Chacón-Torrico <hchacont@uw.edu>
Authors@R: c(
    person("Horacio", "Chacón-Torrico", , "hchacont@uw.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: Provides a comprehensive interface to Peru's CKAN data portal 
    (datosabiertos.gob.pe), enabling users to query and search datasets, 
    extract metadata, and download resources directly into R. The package 
    offers functions for catalog exploration, smart data downloading, and 
    seamless integration with R data analysis workflows.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/horaciochacon/peruopen, https://horaciochacon.github.io/peruopen/
BugReports: https://github.com/horaciochacon/peruopen/issues
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    httr2,
    jsonlite,
    readr,
    readxl,
    tibble,
    dplyr,
    rlang,
    cli,
    fs,
    memoise,
    rappdirs,
    knitr
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    rmarkdown,
    quarto
